<section class="market-pro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-b413da4baf72?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Team collaboration">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="badge">YOUR TRUSTED DENVER MARKETING PARTNERS</div>
      <h2>WHY DENVER BUSINESSES CHOOSE OUR MARKETING PROS</h2>
      <p>
        We're not just another agency. We're <strong>Denver marketing pros</strong> and locals who 
        understand the market, know the neighborhoods, and have the relationships that get 
        results. Our clients choose us because we deliver measurable outcomes, transparent 
        reporting, and personalized service that treats your business like our own. From <strong>web 
        design to PPC campaigns</strong>, we've got you covered.
      </p>
      <button class="cta-button">GET STARTED TODAY</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .market-pro {
    background: #FFFDF1;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .content {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 60px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #000;
  }

  p {
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .cta-button {
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #000;
    color: #FFFDF1;
  }

  .image {
    flex: 1;
    align-self: stretch;
    min-height: 500px;
  }

  .image img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .image {
      min-height: 300px;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
